Subject: RE: [VB] Reduction box half removal

It's press in, like a freeze plug.  To remove use a stud puller at a body
shop, pops right out.  Clean everything up, and use a sealant prior to
pressing/tapping back in.  I used Loctite sleeve retainer, has held up 5
years.  Where on the East Coast?

